  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/c2066a5011f494332449bd7c2e03b1aa.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You know how cats always love to run away? Well, you have to look for them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/b1c1f37d6f45aa1239addb9e84b76686.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Idyllic cats: japan is a first-person 3D game, you run for the character and look for cats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal of the game is to find all 100 cats, but it is not so easy, because each cat has its own characteristics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/a95586dfb247082b9aa76bc527a7ec92.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/ac6ccb008405fbdee932a48a1d4945ec.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Coop up to 4 people. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Competitive speed mode for friends, who can find cats the fastest?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/426c6b7e032acb2bf9f6a418a4317d74.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/1a410b94602f188401a1237dcaf8624f.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Customize your character as you wish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/9473cc648cb6cd0dd65e6af2e4ec274d.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/e304e1c763167d2c725c8332d54efd3c.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Cats will constantly run to new shelters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Each cat has its own behavior and its own favorite places.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/fb84fbf42b7a1deb0401eb8596cad5df.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/ff9164dc52ee96887ac408c6058327bf.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Get tips on where to look for cats from NPCs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Find all 100 cats!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/c2066a5011f494332449bd7c2e03b1aa.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You know how cats always love to run away? Well, you have to look for them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/b1c1f37d6f45aa1239addb9e84b76686.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Idyllic cats: japan is a first-person 3D game, you run for the character and look for cats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal of the game is to find all 100 cats, but it is not so easy, because each cat has its own characteristics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/a95586dfb247082b9aa76bc527a7ec92.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/ac6ccb008405fbdee932a48a1d4945ec.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=220 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Coop up to 4 people. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Competitive speed mode for friends, who can find cats the fastest?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/426c6b7e032acb2bf9f6a418a4317d74.avif?t=1754291290\" width=614 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672980/extras/1a410b94602f188401a1237dcaf8624f.a